metadata.name: MEV Burn #1
metadata.description:
Ethereum is getting yet another economic upgrade! The scarcity engine is getting a massive level up with the advent of the MEV Burn.

With Justin Drake and Dom, a core developer at the Ethereum Foundation, they walk us through the research and reasoning behind this next major upgrade.

Just when we thought we couldn’t get any more bullish…

ETH will become even more ultra sound.

Art generated from the quote at [1:25:30 - 1:26:00] where Justin Drake describes how ETH needs to become pristine collateral in order to fulfill its roll as money in the internet of value. 

10% of proceeds donated to ultrasound.eth
